{"prompt": "Generate a website for a smart home technology. The website should be minimalist and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Smart Home Tech</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #e53935;\n            --secondary-color: #f8bbad;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --header-text-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--header-text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        main {\n            flex: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom right, var(--brand-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--background-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 800px;\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--header-text-color);\n        }\n\n        p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--background-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--background-color);\n            border-color: var(--background-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: auto;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Smart Living</h1>\n    </header>\n    <main>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Your Home, Smarter.</h2>\n            <p>Experience the future of home automation with our cutting-edge smart technology. Seamlessly control your lighting, security, climate, and entertainment with a single touch or voice command.</p>\n            <a href=\"#learn-more\" class=\"cta-button\">Discover More</a>\n        </div>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Smart Living. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}